      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct engagement to the rear-mounted limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and inspection of the rear subframe for structural integrity. The suspension architecture remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for superior lateral grip. While the aesthetics show light patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust and track-capable.",
